com.rpfsoftwares.systembuilderlib.database

Class JContentValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rpfsoftwares.systembuilderlib.database.JContentValues

  • public class JContentValues
extends java.lang.Object
    A different implementation of the HashMap class; Based on Android's ContentValues class; Used to bind values to corresponding keys.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Rosário Pereira Fernandes
